## 사건 정보

**사건명**: DICK BURNS, INC. v. B & H SALES, INC.
**판결일**: 1974-05-24
**법원**: District Court of Appeal of Florida
**관할**: Florida, FL

**판사**: John, Mager, Moore, Walden

## 변호인

Raymond B. Ray and Joseph Easthope, Ferrero, Middlebrooks & Houston, Fort Lauderdale, for appellant., Fred C. Davant and G. Victor Tutan, Wicker, Smith, Pyszka, Blomqvist & Dav-ant, Miami, and Donald J. Sasser and John C. Randolph of Johnston, Liliethal & Johnston, West Palm Beach, for appellee-B & H Sales, Inc., Richard G. Gordon, McCune, Hiaasen, Crum, Ferris & Gardner, Fort Lauderdale, for appellee-Continental Oil Co.

## 인용

- 295 So. 2d 344

## 판결문 요약


PER CURIAM.
It does not appear that the trial court abused its discretion in dismissing this cause for lack of prosecution under the circumstances reflected in the record. Reddish v. Forlines, 207 So.2d 703 (1st D.C.A.Fla.1968).
Affirmed.
WALDEN and MAGER, JJ., and MOORE, JOHN H., II, Associate Judge, concur.
